Introduction

OuiOui (Korean: 위위) is a South Korean duet under Inplanet Music, consisting of Blueny and Meijee. Their name means "Yes, Yes in French"; they wanted to make music that people could relate to and think “yes, yes”. They debuted on March 15, 2018 with the single “Hana”.
